  "original_title": "\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0da7\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0ddd \u0d9c\u0dd1\u0dc3\u0dca \u0dbb\u0dd4.50 \u0d9a\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca \u0d89\u0dc4\u0dc5\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Litro gas up by Rs.50",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Litro domestic gas distribution will start from today (11) in Colombo and suburbs and on the 13th of this month to outlying provinces, said a senior Litro company official.",
        "The official mentioned that consumers are being asked to submit their May electricity bills this year to avoid people gathering and queuing and that a 12.5 kg gas cylinder within Colombo costs only Rs 4,910.",
        "Accordingly, the price of a gas cylinder, which was 4860 rupees, has been increased by 50 rupees."
      ],
